Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.90,0:22:25.04,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}そう　大事に開くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.17,0:22:36.76,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}日が暮れて帰り道
